[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr]  ## Features
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Mock Test Tracker** — Log mock test scores and track band progress over time
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr]  
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Daily Plan** — Plan and track daily study tasks across all IELTS skills
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Progress Analytics** — Charts and stats for study days, hours, skill balance, and band trends
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Grammar Notes** — Organize grammar topics with examples and common mistakes
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +  <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/PRs-welcome-brightgreen" alt="PRs welcome"/>
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Import/Export** — JSON import/export for backup and migration
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **AI Assistant** — Optional OpenAI-compatible API integration for feedback and suggestions
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Global Search** — Full-text search across all your data
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Dark Mode** — Light/dark theme toggle
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 📚 Vocabulary Management
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Offline-First PWA** — Works offline after initial load; data stored in IndexedDB
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 📖 Skill Tracking
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Skill Tracking** — Log reading, listening, writing, and speaking practice sessions
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +SM-2 spaced repetition system with tagging, filtering, and review queues. Track vocabulary from multiple sources — manual entry, browser extension, or AI-assisted enrichment.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 📓 Mistake Notebook
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 📅 Daily Study Plan
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Vocabulary Management** — Add, tag, filter, and review words with spaced repetition (SM-2)
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **Mistake Notebook** — Record and review mistakes with correction tracking
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Log mock test scores (overall band + skill bands) and track progress over time with trend visualizations.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 🎯 Mock Test Tracker
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Record mistakes with corrections and explanations. Mistakes are tracked by skill and surfaced for review based on frequency and recency.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Log practice sessions across all four IELTS skills (Reading, Listening, Writing, Speaking) plus Grammar. Each session is timestamped and tagged by skill for progress analytics.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Weakness detection** — Identifies lowest-accuracy skills
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Auto-generated daily plans based on weaknesses, due reviews, and user preferences. Plans adapt to available study time and exam proximity.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 📊 Progress Analytics
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Next-best-action** — Priority-ranked study recommendations
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Daily plan generation** — Personalized daily study task lists
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Core business logic engine that drives:
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Proactive local messages (due reviews, weak skills, exam countdown, study streak)
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Messenger-style AI assistant with:
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Charts and stats for total study days, hours per skill, skill balance distribution, band trends, study streak, and weekly reflections.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Configurable AI provider (OpenAI-compatible)
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Chat interface with conversation memory
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 🧠 Learning Journey Engine
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Context-aware responses using learning engine data
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Review scheduling** — SM-2 for vocabulary, frequency-based for mistakes
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Built-in IELTS reading passages, listening transcripts, and vocabulary lists. Content is versioned and seeded on first run with incremental updates.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +AI-powered and rule-based exercise generation for grammar and vocabulary practice. Exercises are scored and mistakes are automatically saved to the Mistake Notebook.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 📖 Content Library
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Save vocabulary, phrases, sentences via right-click or floating toolbar
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 🤖 AI Tutor Chat
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Mini AI tutor popup
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Bridge protocol for syncing with the web app
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### ✍️ Exercise Generator
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- AI explanations for selected text
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 🔄 Import / Export
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Full JSON backup and restore with merge and replace modes. Schema validation on import prevents data corruption.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 📱 PWA Support
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 🌐 Browser Extension
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Light, dark, and system theme with CSS custom property design tokens.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.725Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- YouTube transcript helper for listening practice
