[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +├── context/              # React contexts (settings, theme)
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +```
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +├── models/               # Domain model type definitions
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +├── data/                 # Data seeding definitions
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +├── types/                # Shared TypeScript types
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +├── utils/                # App-level utilities
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### Data Flow
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   └── ...               # Other features
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Component → Custom Hook → Feature Service → Repository (IndexedDB/localStorage)
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.727Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
