[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] -### Data Architecture
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] -All user data is stored client-side:
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] -
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **IndexedDB** — Vocabulary, tasks, journal entries, mock tests, reviews, grammar notes, mistakes, and topic progress
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] -- **localStorage** — App settings (theme, target band, API key, etc.)
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] +## Data Architecture
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] +All user data is stored **client-side only** — no backend, no cloud sync, no telemetry:
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] -| `pnpm test`           | Run tests (Vitest)                 |
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] -| `pnpm lint`           | Lint source code (ESLint)          |
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] +|---------|----------|
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Storage | Contents |
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| **localStorage** | Settings (theme, target band, AI API key, preferences) |
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr]  Data flows through a layered architecture:
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr]  ```
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] -| `pnpm dev`            | Start development server           |
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr]  
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr]  
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| **IndexedDB** | Vocabulary, study sessions, logs, grammar notes, mistakes, progress, chat history |
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Component → Custom Hook → Feature Service → Repository → IndexedDB
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.729Z] [INFO] [stderr] -
