[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr] +## Privacy
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **No backend** — all data stays in your browser
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **AI features are opt-in** — you must provide your own API key
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Only explicitly selected text** is sent to the AI API
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Full data export and deletion** available via Settings → Data Management
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr] -Please ensure your code passes linting and tests before submitting.
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **Extension permissions** are minimal — only what's needed for collecting text and optional YouTube transcript access
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **No analytics, telemetry, or tracking** — zero data leaves your device
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr] -Project Link: [https://github.com/<your-username>/ielts-journey](https://github.com/<your-username>/ielts-journey)
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr]  
[2026-07-02T04:00:27.731Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- **API key** is stored in `localStorage` only, never sent anywhere except the configured AI endpoint
